text: Kendall Francis Schmidt (born November 2, 1990) is an American singer- songwriter, music producer and actor. He played Kendall Knight in Big Time Rush, Easy A With Getaway The Frozen Ground and is a current member of the boyband with the same name.Kendall Schmidt . staree.com ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:American pop singers Category:American pianists Category:American drummers Category:American bass guitarists Category:American record producers Category:American singer- songwriters Category:Singers from Wichita, Kansas Category:Musicians from Wichita, Kansas Category:Actors from Wichita, Kansas Category:Writers from Wichita, Kansas Category:Big Time Rush members
